Qh over Th plus minus Qc over
Tc because of this inequality

00:07:03.330 --> 00:07:06.811
writing it as less
than or equal to 0.

00:07:06.811 --> 00:07:09.090
OK?

00:07:09.090 --> 00:07:11.510
What does that tell us?

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:13.620
As it stands, not much.

00:07:13.620 --> 00:07:17.660
But then I promised you
