00:07:17.660 --> 00:07:23.090
then this is an example of
a much more powerful result,

00:07:23.090 --> 00:07:25.380
which is the Clausius Theorem.

00:07:25.380 --> 00:07:28.900
So let's start with writing
what that theorem is

00:07:28.900 --> 00:07:30.985
and how it relates to
a simple expression.

00:07:37.990 --> 00:07:50.970
And the theory is that
for any cyclic process

00:07:50.970 --> 00:07:54.800
I can, cyclic,
