coordinates in principle

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:03.980
that is used to
describe the system,

00:08:03.980 --> 00:08:06.810
I will start with the
position that is equilibrium,

00:08:06.810 --> 00:08:11.680
so I can put that
point in this state,

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:15.280
but then I make
a transformation.

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:17.440
And ultimately
return to that point.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:20.420
So the cycle is the
return to that point.

00:08:20.420 --> 00:08:23.160
So I carry out a set of steps.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:26.550
And I haven't indicated
the set of steps

00:08:26.550 --> 00:08:30.100
