the possibility therefore

00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:40.520
that some of the times
these elements dQ

00:09:40.520 --> 00:09:44.400
will be negative just as I
did over here by writing this

00:09:44.400 --> 00:09:48.650
as minus Qc so
