00:23:06.830 --> 00:23:13.790
to B, dQ, reversible
over T, over some path,

00:23:13.790 --> 00:23:19.362
and the answer is going to
be the same for doing it

00:23:19.362 --> 00:23:20.320
along a different path.

00:23:27.780 --> 00:23:32.390
Because if I went
