is the Gibbs free energy, G,

00:54:53.060 --> 00:54:57.270
which is the energy minus ts.

00:54:57.270 --> 00:55:02.890
This part is the Helmholtz
free energy, minus Jixi.

00:55:09.760 --> 00:55:16.010
And that if I regard this as
a function of state, which

00:55:16.010 --> 00:55:21.445
certainly will be minimized
under conditions of constant J

00:55:21.445 --> 00:55:25.280
and T for some constraint
