00:55:25.280 --> 00:55:28.130
Quite generally as
a state function

00:55:28.130 --> 00:55:30.420
depending on all
of these variables,

00:55:30.420 --> 00:55:35.000
it's variations
would be able to be

00:55:35.000 --> 00:55:41.188
expressed as minus
SdT minus Jidxi.

00:55:44.394 --> 00:55:50.162
ie, our G is naturally a
function of temperature

00:55:50.162 --> 00:55:51.370
and the set of displacements.

