00:58:24.170 --> 00:58:26.790
I have so many molecules
of oxygen and nitrogen,

00:58:26.790 --> 00:58:32.870
or whatever is the composition,
but then we sort of start

00:58:32.870 --> 00:58:35.140
to get into the realm of
chemistry and the fact

00:58:35.140 --> 00:58:38.000
that the different chemical
components can start

00:58:38.000 --> 00:58:42.040
to react with each
