00:58:52.460 --> 00:58:54.590
something that is a variable.

00:58:54.590 --> 00:58:59.850
And in order to specify
exactly what the energy

00:58:59.850 --> 00:59:03.210
content of a system
is you have to specify

00:59:03.210 --> 00:59:05.750
how many particles
and the energy

00:59:05.750 --> 00:59:08.010
carried by those particles.

00:59:08.010 --> 00:59:12.540
So the list of things
that appears here,

00:59:12.540 --> 00:59:16.970
especially when you think in
terms of chemical systems,

00:59:16.970 --> 00:59:20.045
has an additional
element that is typically

00:59:20.045 --> 00:59:20.920
called chemical work.

00:59:25.110 --> 00:59:31.470
And so let's separate mechanical
work from the chemical work.

00:59:31.470 --> 00:59:38.090
So mechanical work
was sum over iJidxi

00:59:38.090 --> 00:59:40.750
where these were
real displacements

00:59:40.750 --> 00:59:44.100
and we can actually
write an expression that

00:59:44.100 --> 00:59:49.880
is very similar here where
the displacements are

00:59:49.880 --> 00:59:52.520
the number of particles
of different species,

00:59:52.520 --> 00:59:56.740
allowing potentially there
going to other species

00:59:56.740 --> 01:00:00.550
through chemical reactions
provided we multiply these

01:00:00.550 --> 01:00:04.300
