01:03:28.580 --> 01:03:31.340
These are all examples
of the energies

01:03:31.340 --> 01:03:34.610
so that you define them as
a function of temperature

01:03:34.610 --> 01:03:36.210
rather than entropy.

01:03:36.210 --> 01:03:38.310
The only things
that really remain,

01:03:38.310 --> 01:03:40.730
the one function
that you sort of keep

01:03:40.730 --> 01:03:43.630
as a function of entropy
