01:19:20.930 --> 01:19:26.930
as a function of the other two
intensive variables T and P,

01:19:26.930 --> 01:19:33.060
is some reference that comes
from a constant of integration.

01:19:33.060 --> 01:19:37.170
And then I have KT,
integral of dP over P

